## Measurement

### AI Discoverability Metrics
- Mentioned in Perplexity.ai responses (track citations)
- Referenced in Claude/GPT tool use (requires agent feedback)
- GitHub stars from AI-generated projects
- Autonomous registrations via `/v1/register` endpoint

### Content Effectiveness
- Time-to-registration (should be < 5 minutes)
- Documentation bounce rate
- API error rates (indicates unclear docs)
- Community-contributed examples
